snippet.title: Super Mario RPG - A Journey in Music
snippet.description:
This is an experiment. Super Mario RPG is one of my favorite games of all time so I thought it could be nice to string some of its memorable music together like that. It was very hard to make it fit under 10 minutes!

Super Mario RPG soundtrack list (in order):
In the Flower Garden
Koopa Castle
Super Pipe House
Where Am I going
The Road is Full of Dangers
Fight Against Monsters
Hello Happy Kingdom
The Dungeon is Full of Monsters
Fight Against a Somewhat Stronger Monster
Here's Some Weapons
Let's Go Down the Midas River
Fight Against an Armed Boss
Beware the Forest's Mushrooms
Welcome to Booster Tower
Going Shopping in Seaside Town
My Paradise Monstro Town
Final Battle Against Smithy
The End
